name: Lost in a Dreamscape
description: This interactive experience created by Ani Dalal emulates the feeling of being lost  in dreams, mazes and doomscrolls, and invites the  users/participants to interact with an imaginary ecosystem. It presents users with a fictional world consisting of interactive elements that do not follow the usual principles of the interfaces people generally engage with on a daily basis.
